  "epitaph": "You offered the world a pair of silicon wings,\nTo guide the cursor where the future sings.\nBut the docs grew stagnant, the pages unmoved,\nTwo years of silence, a feat unimproved.\nThough twenty-three thousand stars lit the grey,\nThe repo was locked and put away.\nSo close the book on the code pilot\u2019s tale,\nRest in peace, exit 0.",
